# macOS/iCloud "filename 2.ext" duplicate-on-conflict copies. This project dir
# sits under an iCloud-synced Documents folder; a stray auto-commit swept a batch
# of these into git once (reverted in c3f3a13). Keep them out for good — both the
# file form ("foo 2.ext") and the EXTENSIONLESS dir/file form ("broker 2",
# "approvals 3") iCloud also creates for directories.
* [0-9].*
* [0-9][0-9].*
* [0-9]
* [0-9][0-9]

# Harness / local config
.claude/

# Local-only planning docs (kept private, not published)
evaluation.md
build-prompts.md
# Build-process plans (agentic-worker scaffolding) — kept locally, not published.
# The published design record lives in docs/design/specs/.
docs/design/plans/

# Stray editor/harness temp files
_tmp_*

# Security-skim PoC harnesses — gitignored but referenced by the findings doc
security/poc/
